public class ImageUploadEditWidget
extends com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.FormPanel
implements ch.unifr.pai.twice.module.client.TWICEModule<ImageUploadEditWidget>

A component that allows to upload files (e.g. images) to the server and making them available as notes. Notice: This is a very simple module that doesn't make use of a lot of resources. Therefore, the component implements the interface TWICEModule by itself. Nevertheless, for more complex modules, this is not a recommended way of implementation since the benefits of lazy loading are evicted.

Author:
Oliver Schmid
